description: [CookieMiner](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0492) has used python scripts on the user’s system, as well as the Python variant of the [Empire](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S0363) agent, EmPyre.(Citation: Unit42 CookieMiner Jan 2019)
